<h2>
You've selected <%= params['number'] %> (<%= params['city'] %>)
as your JMP number
</h2>

<p>
Please enter your <a href="../faq/#jabber">Jabber</a> ID and press Submit (a
Jabber ID normally looks like an email address, of the form user@example.com).
A message will be sent to you to allow you to complete registration from your
Jabber client.
</p>

<form action="" method="post">
<input type="hidden" name="number" value="<%= params['number'] %>" />
<label>Jabber ID: <input type="text" name="jid" /></label>
<button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
